{"tid":1533412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點忍","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:13:09.000Z","uid":10292,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"19ad298f6f2e6fe8ad6caf49a35286bd34598ed5","tid":1533412,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"有個藍絲雄性生我出黎嘅仆街響屋企<br />\n都知佢無人性<br />\n我之前情緒病死唔去執返條命仔<br />\n個陣佢都話唔會阻我去死<br />\n平時我唔會同佢有交流<br />\n今日屋企附近有人企跳<br />\n我落樓去幫手搵<br />\n返到黎佢第一句問死左未？<br />\n我忍唔撚到同佢嘈<br />\n我發現佢真係完全無人性<br />\n啱啱我喊到仆街佢仲煸風點火<br />\n放心收尾個幾年佢一定過得好撚慘<br />\n<br />\n問題來了<br />\n我準備讀asso year 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無自己房之餘佢每日響我隔離係咁噏<br />\n我抗壓能力差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂唔順了<br />\n好唔好quit asso出黎搵野做搬出去"},{"pid":"2e4f9e93c17298fdc5f5259542b895e8e9a2ffe4","tid":1533412,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"當佢廢噏 唔好理佢<br />\n唔係忍唔忍既問題<br />\n係你無必要對住屋企人動火勞氣<br />\n巴打加油"},{"pid":"8a552390cf06fab827043c4760da0839cfe3d58a","tid":1533412,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"又係方仲賢bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ea1735503a0e1f37394d20f6d547f1cc76065a","tid":1533412,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"其實繼續讀asso都心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為知道會好難行<br />\n估唔到未開學就行唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57953ef741cc9a83e08cd1ce3a5d07681968713","tid":1533412,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/153